WEBVTT

00:00:00.585 --> 00:00:04.798
UNK gevezn, vu hobn zey JEMAND gekumen UNK di farmegn

00:00:05.057 --> 00:00:08.055
zenen gegangen di polyakn hobn geharget di mentshn

00:00:09.276 --> 00:00:11.416
un zenen gekumen keyn Kroke

00:00:11.416 --> 00:00:16.807
hobn zey gekumen keyn BOZEGO CIALA, JOZEFINSKI, DIETLOWSKI. dort gevezn

00:00:16.807 --> 00:00:25.739
g- dort gevezn di yidishe gegnt, un dort gekumen, un vemen hobn zey getrofn, hobn zey dort geshosn fun di yidn vos zenen tsurikgekumen nebekh fun di lagers.

00:00:25.932 --> 00:00:29.902
undz ho'mir nisht gevoynt in di gegnt. undz ho'mir gevoynt oyf di lange gas

00:00:29.902 --> 00:00:34.092
zenen a sakh yidn gekumen tsu loyfn tsu undz in di WOHNUNG arayn. nokh dem pogrom

00:00:34.092 --> 00:00:38.109
hobn mir nokh gevart a bisele. di mame hot gevart nokh a bisele oyf gelt

00:00:38.301 --> 00:00:41.872
un bald hobn mir zikh genumen tsu geyn keyn Tshekhn

00:00:41.912 --> 00:00:43.290
⟨ale avek⟩ fun dort

00:00:43.414 --> 00:00:48.111
vayl mir hobn nisht gekent vartn azoy lang oyf di AFFIDAVIT, vayl

00:00:48.111 --> 00:00:53.263
oyf di kvote, vayl dos iz nisht gevezn meglekh, zenen mir geganen keyn Tshekhn, ⟨hobn mir⟩ geganen, geforn

00:00:53.438 --> 00:00:55.254
in a dorf arayn

00:00:56.357 --> 00:01:04.130
un dort hot men opgekoyft a goye mit a mentsh vos hot gefirt, un hot oyfgehoybn di drotn, zenen mir aroyf- adurkhgeganen keyn BRATISLAVA

00:01:04.558 --> 00:01:07.623
un fun BRATISLAVA zenen mir dort gevezn a bisele

00:01:08.203 --> 00:01:10.475
ze'mir vider gevezn in JOINT

00:01:10.617 --> 00:01:13.091
fun anfang ongekumen in JOINT arayn

00:01:13.468 --> 00:01:16.230
un shpeter hot men zikh gedungen a shtub, hobn mir gevoynt

00:01:16.230 --> 00:01:18.120
neyn, tsun ersht bin ikh ongekumen

00:01:18.173 --> 00:01:21.073
tsu EBERSTARK, ⟨veys nisht⟩ tsi hostu gekent EBERSTARKn?

00:01:21.568 --> 00:01:22.810
yo, kenst zi.

00:01:23.104 --> 00:01:26.017
zi voynt in Daytshland ⟨bay dem kleyns⟩

00:01:26.192 --> 00:01:27.738
shoyn, iz nisht a khilek

00:01:27.745 --> 00:01:32.717
zey hobn ge- zey zenen gevezn bahaltn fun geto, zenen antlofn keyn

00:01:33.212 --> 00:01:35.990
keyn U- Ungarn

00:01:36.823 --> 00:01:40.480
gevezn oykhet oyf ⟨MONTELUPI⟩, hot gehat

00:01:40.480 --> 00:01:42.560
iz geven zeyer a raykher mentsh, der

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:44.850
EBERSTARK, Arn EBERSTARK

00:01:44.850 --> 00:01:47.290
un hot er gehat SCHMUCK

00:01:47.775 --> 00:01:53.872
un iz gele- m'hot im gekhapt fun bunker in geto, hot men gekhapt im in bunker, iz er gekumen oyf di O.D.

00:01:53.872 --> 00:01:57.146
hot er gezogt "her tsu, ikh hob dia- a diamant"

00:01:57.146 --> 00:01:59.126
iz er geganen, un

00:01:59.757 --> 00:02:03.980
⟨dort eyner⟩, un geganen tsu a yeke un hot im aroy- hot gezogt "yo, gut.

00:02:03.980 --> 00:02:05.520
kh'loz dikh aroys."

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:08.933
hot gehat ungarishe papirn, hot men im aroysgelozt

00:02:08.933 --> 00:02:11.242
un er hot gevust az er iz do mit

00:02:11.417 --> 00:02:15.005
ts- di froy mit tsvey kinder, a tokhter mit a zun

00:02:15.889 --> 00:02:17.632
hot er gezogt azoy. "neyn.

00:02:17.632 --> 00:02:20.247
nor dray mentshn kenen aroysgeyn far dem shteyn."

00:02:20.247 --> 00:02:22.197
s'iz nisht genug vert far im gevezn.

00:02:22.197 --> 00:02:26.838
hot er gezogt "⟨kh'geb⟩ dir nokh a sh- shteyn, un ⟨lomir⟩ aroys di tokhter oykh." hot er aroysgelozt di tokhter

00:02:26.838 --> 00:02:29.138
zenen ale avek nokh Ungarn.

00:02:29.372 --> 00:02:31.610
un ir zent tsu zey gekumen.

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:31.178
un ikh bin

00:02:31.178 --> 00:02:36.568
ikh bin tsu zey gekumen keyn, kh'hob gevust az zenen in, zey zenen fun Ungarn shoyn s- gekumen keyn Tshekhn

00:02:36.628 --> 00:02:39.418
un ikh bin gekumen tsu zey keyn Tshekhn, bin ikh dort a

00:02:39.418 --> 00:02:44.458
a por tog gevezn, biz di mame iz gekumen tsu forn, vayl ikh bin tsun ersht gekumen fun Poyln aroys

00:02:44.458 --> 00:02:45.904
mit mayn shvester

00:02:46.281 --> 00:02:49.127
un bin bay im gevezn, hob ikh dort getrofn

00:02:49.133 --> 00:02:51.152
mentshn zitsn baym tish.

00:02:51.462 --> 00:02:53.515
dos iz shoyn gevezn JAHRE

00:02:54.145 --> 00:02:56.029
zeks un fertsik, yo?

00:02:56.608 --> 00:03:02.052
zeks un, kh'hob gezen mentshn baym tish, un hot men ongehoybn ts- azoy tsu redn fun di krig, ahin un aher

00:03:02.312 --> 00:03:03.625
hob ikh

00:03:03.625 --> 00:03:08.482
gegebn a zog, er iz ⟨dokh⟩ nisht gevezn in krig, un EBERSTARK, er hot zikh dokh nisht gekent onrufn

00:03:08.792 --> 00:03:12.988
un ikh hob mikh azoy ongerufn der vos hot ongetun a hitele oyfn kop

00:03:13.112 --> 00:03:15.148
darf men shisn

00:03:16.656 --> 00:03:18.759
zogt er "vos zogstu azoy o?"

00:03:19.474 --> 00:03:22.274
vayl der vos hot dort getrogn a hitele

00:03:22.274 --> 00:03:28.664
hot ⟨ongetun⟩, ⟨ot der⟩ man muz tsushteln mentshn, un az er hot tsugeshtelt mentshn, hot er dem mentsh oyf di nemones

00:03:28.664 --> 00:03:31.007
darf men im shisn, azoy UNK vi der yeke.

00:03:31.007 --> 00:03:32.877
gornisht keyn untershid gevezn.

00:03:33.193 --> 00:03:35.848
shoyn, dem, iz di mentshn zenen avekgeganen

00:03:35.848 --> 00:03:43.028
un shpeter ruft mikh tsu Arn der kuzin, ruft men im tsu, zogt er "veyst ver ⟨do iz do⟩ gezesn?" zog ikh "vo- i- ver iz gezesn, KNOBLOCH?"

00:03:43.028 --> 00:03:47.868
ershtn veys ikh nisht ver iz der KNOBLOCH. ikh hob gevust velekhe kapo, vi er heyst, der kapo?

00:03:47.925 --> 00:03:52.171
veyst er nisht vel- ⟨na⟩ az er hot ongetun dos hitele, kumt im oykhet a koyl in kop arayn.

00:03:53.950 --> 00:03:55.547
kh'hob mikh gornisht geshemt.

00:03:56.110 --> 00:04:00.204
vi azoy hot zikh bashlosn az ir kumt keyn Antverpn?

00:04:00.244 --> 00:04:04.642
s'iz azoy gevezn. fun dort, fun BRATISLAVA, zenen mir geforn keyn PRAG.

00:04:05.138 --> 00:04:13.888
in PRAG zenen mir vider gevezn a tsayt, a bisele in JOINT. shpeter hot men zikh gedungen a shtub bay goyim, ze'mir gevezn ⟨vayl in⟩ JOINT ken men nisht azoy lang zitsn.

00:04:14.183 --> 00:04:15.623
ze'mir gevezn

00:04:15.623 --> 00:04:21.816
un ze'mir zikh gedreyt. mir ho'mir alts geha- -vart oyf di AFFIDAVIT, zol men krign a, tsu forn keyn Amerike

00:04:21.816 --> 00:04:24.859
yednfals, ⟨iz⟩ gezen az s'kumt nisht azoy shnel

00:04:25.101 --> 00:04:27.575
ho'mir ⟨zikh⟩ gezogt m'vet forn vayter.

00:04:27.615 --> 00:04:29.735
ze'mir geforn keyn Pariz.

00:04:30.822 --> 00:04:32.486
far vos keyn Pariz?

00:04:32.239 --> 00:04:37.515
vayl fun Pariz hot geheysn az me ken shneler forn UNK AFFIDAVIT keyn Amerike.

00:04:38.702 --> 00:04:44.612
iz hobn mir zikh shoyn gevolt ⟨instalirn⟩ ergets zayn oyf a plats. nisht yedes muz zayn in do un dort, un dort do

00:04:44.612 --> 00:04:47.772
un dos kost dokh a farmegn gelt. dos gelt vet zikh oyslozn.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:52.485
ho'mir zikh gevolt ergets ⟨instalirn⟩. ze'mir geforn keyn Pariz, ze'mir tsugekumen tsum JOINT

00:04:52.485 --> 00:04:56.347
vider dos zelbe. undz ho'mir gekrign dort bakantshaft UND SO WEITER

00:04:56.556 --> 00:04:58.845
un zeyer fayne mentshn gevezn

00:04:59.070 --> 00:05:00.650
un ho'mir

00:05:01.078 --> 00:05:04.338
es iz gevezn far di yontoyvim, rosheshone, azoy vi d-

00:05:04.338 --> 00:05:06.338
haynt, iz dos for di yontoyvim

00:05:06.338 --> 00:05:08.586
un ken men dokh nisht blaybn in ho-

00:05:08.586 --> 00:05:11.806
UNK iz a yidishe kehile un kosher un, un ales

00:05:11.806 --> 00:05:16.060
s'iz vayt tsugegan, nisht keyn davenen, nisht keyn gornisht, hobn mir geklert

00:05:16.060 --> 00:05:19.044
hot men undz JEMAND gezogt "veyst vos? kum keyn Antverpn."

00:05:19.354 --> 00:05:21.575
Antverpn iz a yidisher plats.

00:05:22.172 --> 00:05:29.522
⟨er⟩ vet dos hobn a besmedresh, vest dokh shoyn epes dort trefn bakantshaft, UNK un shpeter hobn mir gehat do Binem ⟨GUTTER⟩. kh'veys nisht tsi UNK, MADAME ⟨GUTTER⟩

00:05:29.522 --> 00:05:31.202
UNK's foter

00:05:31.318 --> 00:05:32.631
MADAME ⟨GUTTER⟩

00:05:32.631 --> 00:05:40.161
hobn mir gehat, un ze'mir tsugeforn takesh keyn Antverpn, zenen mir gekumen oyf di PELIKAAN ⟨STRASSE⟩ mit di tsug, on a papir, on a gornisht

00:05:40.161 --> 00:05:41.791
hobn mir gornisht gehat

00:05:41.848 --> 00:05:45.262
oyf shvarts, ales oyf shvarts. az do iz arayngekumen der

00:05:45.262 --> 00:05:49.572
 CONDUCTEUR ⟨mener⟩, zenen mir geganen oyf yene zayt, vayl keyn papirn hobn mir nisht gehat.

00:05:49.572 --> 00:05:53.682
keyn DOUANE hobn mir nisht gekent UNK, vayl mir hobn nisht gehat keyn aynfor, gornisht.

00:05:54.100 --> 00:05:59.797
zenen mir gekumen oyf di PELIKAAN STRASSE, hobn mir shoyn getrofn yidn, hobn mir zey gefregt "vu iz MONSIEUR ⟨GUTTER⟩?"

00:05:59.803 --> 00:06:04.724
hot men undz gezogt bay UNK er hot khasene gehat, ⟨ze'mir⟩ tsugeganen tsu zey

00:06:04.765 --> 00:06:09.349
hot undz bald genumen. der UNK iz a herlekher mentsh gevezn, a yidisher mentsh

00:06:09.405 --> 00:06:12.521
hot undz bald gezogt yontoyvim vet ets zayn bay undz

00:06:12.595 --> 00:06:16.225
iz ze'mir geblibn bay im takesh, ⟨oder⟩ shpeter iz di mame nokh gekumen

00:06:16.225 --> 00:06:20.915
vayl ikh bin gekumen tsun ersht mit mayn shvester. shpeter iz di mame nokh gekumen, ze'mir takesh do gevezn.

00:06:20.919 --> 00:06:25.531
shpeter hobn mir zikh gedungen a WOHNUNG oyf di ⟨MUIZEN⟩ STRASSE, nisht keyn groyse ⟨tsen⟩ zakhn

00:06:26.095 --> 00:06:29.076
hobn mir zikh ⟨gekrign⟩ a WOHNUNG, a shtibele

00:06:29.352 --> 00:06:30.780
mit a kokh

00:06:31.140 --> 00:06:34.323
un mir ho'mir gehat groyse nisim mit dem shtibele mit a kokh

00:06:34.448 --> 00:06:36.433
vayl s'iz gevezn ale tsuzamen

00:06:37.165 --> 00:06:38.875
un shabes hot men

00:06:38.875 --> 00:06:40.534
gelozt gaz brenen

00:06:41.468 --> 00:06:43.639
un di gas iz ongeganen.

00:06:44.607 --> 00:06:51.165
keyn shank hobn mir nisht gehat, vayl zenen mir dokh gevezn nokh fremd, hobn mir nisht gehat keyn shank, hobn mir gehat nor di tsvey betn gekoyft

00:06:51.660 --> 00:06:55.960
un, un, un, un a z- un a nets hobn mir gehat hengen

00:06:55.960 --> 00:06:59.530
frukhtn oyfn fentster UNK ayzkastn nisht gevezn

00:06:59.530 --> 00:07:06.270
oyfn fentster gehat hengen frukhtn. oyf eyn mol shtey ikh oyf, zog ikh "mame, der kop tut mir vey. ikh ken nisht oyshaltn." zogt zi "veyst vos?

00:07:06.270 --> 00:07:07.989
gey makh oyf dos fentster."

00:07:08.113 --> 00:07:12.528
gey ⟨ikh⟩ m- makhn oys dos fentster. azoy vi ikh makh ⟨oys dos⟩ fentster, gib ikh a fal anider.

00:07:14.205 --> 00:07:16.291
di gaz iz shoyn gevezn ⟨IMMER⟩.

00:07:16.315 --> 00:07:19.178
gib ikh a fal anider. shteyt oyf di mame

00:07:19.268 --> 00:07:21.692
un di mame vider git zi a fal anider.

00:07:22.322 --> 00:07:24.361
shteyt oykhet dort di shvester

00:07:24.361 --> 00:07:27.736
makht zi, loyft zi oyftsumakhn di tir, un loyft tsu

00:07:27.736 --> 00:07:28.931
di mentshn

00:07:29.005 --> 00:07:32.452
fun nebn vos zey hobn gevoynt, zoln kumen undz helfn.

00:07:32.452 --> 00:07:34.722
zi hot zikh shoyn oysgetsoygn oyf di trepn

00:07:34.722 --> 00:07:36.802
un ze'mir shoyn a- ale azoy ⟨gelegn⟩

00:07:36.802 --> 00:07:40.002
nor s'iz gevezn der mazl az m'hot oyfgemakht ⟨di⟩ fentster

00:07:40.002 --> 00:07:44.017
iz der luft arayngekumen, azoy zenen mir geblibn lebn. dos hobn mir gehat in Belgye.

00:07:46.234 --> 00:07:47.746
ales vos iz bashert.

00:07:48.192 --> 00:07:51.055
un ir hot khasene gehat?

00:07:50.706 --> 00:07:56.302
yo, shpeter. m'hot gekrign, ye, shpeter fun Amerik- fun Amerike hot men undz

00:07:51.263 --> 00:07:54.590
vi hot ir kenen gelernt?

00:07:56.325 --> 00:07:58.242
di mishpokhe erleydikt

00:07:58.249 --> 00:07:59.930
a sheyne WOHNUNG

00:08:00.291 --> 00:08:05.634
vayl do iz nisht gevezn keyn WOHNUNG tsu krign, afile far gelt nisht gevezn, vayl do iz gevezn zeyer bombardirt in Belgye

00:08:05.893 --> 00:08:13.028
oyf di UNK STRASSE, finef hundert tsvontsik. di WOHNUNG iz gevezn komplet ayngerikhtet, mit kristal un mit mebl, ales.

00:08:13.028 --> 00:08:14.665
yidn hobn dort gevoynt

00:08:14.665 --> 00:08:18.392
un zey hobn gelozt azoy farmakhterheyt un ⟨zi iz⟩ azoy geshtanen

00:08:18.550 --> 00:08:21.719
zenen mir geganen tsu do, tsu a mishpokhe, ⟨vos zey hobn⟩ gegebn

00:08:21.719 --> 00:08:24.056
di shlisl. m'hot batsolt dray toyznt f-

00:08:24.056 --> 00:08:27.482
FRANC a, a khoydesh, vos iz gevezn a sakh gelt

00:08:27.482 --> 00:08:28.638
far di WOHNUNG

00:08:28.638 --> 00:08:32.499
ober ⟨mir hobn⟩ zikh genumen a WOHNUNG. s'iz gevezn UNK, zenen mir gevorn mentshn.

00:08:32.961 --> 00:08:34.828
undz ho'mir gevoynt do

00:08:34.969 --> 00:08:40.008
fun zeks un fertsik biz hob ikh khasene, di shvester hot khasene gehat akht un fertsik

00:08:39.998 --> 00:08:41.781
do in Antverpn

00:08:40.099 --> 00:08:40.906
un i-

00:08:40.906 --> 00:08:44.143
in Antverpn, un ikh hob khasene gehat in nayn un fertsik.

00:08:44.183 --> 00:08:46.036
un ver iz geven, ver

00:08:46.036 --> 00:08:48.176
vi hot ir kenen gelernt ayer man?

00:08:48.064 --> 00:08:50.150
a geredter shidekh.

00:08:49.431 --> 00:08:51.433
ver iz er geven?

00:08:51.186 --> 00:08:53.053
er iz gevezn fun CHRZANOW.

00:08:53.481 --> 00:08:55.483
er hot oykh mitgemakht

00:08:54.544 --> 00:09:00.885
⟨er hot di⟩ zelbe krig mitgemakht vi ikh. andere lagers, ABER di zelbe krig gehat. hot gehat a famliye, keyn

00:09:00.885 --> 00:09:04.255
dray briders. ale dray zenen avek. di eltern zenen avek.

00:09:04.255 --> 00:09:05.847
ale mishpokhe iz avek

00:09:05.847 --> 00:09:09.860
iz ⟨EEN⟩ prakhtike mishpokhe. der zeyde iz gevezn bay s-

00:09:09.867 --> 00:09:12.291
baym rebn, a gabe bay

00:09:12.752 --> 00:09:14.535
Tsantser rebe a gabe.

00:09:14.575 --> 00:09:16.779
er iz gevezn a herlekher mentsh UNK

00:09:17.038 --> 00:09:23.107
geshtamen fun herlekhe mentshn, un zenen ale avek. di gantse mishpokhe iz avek. keyner iz nisht geblibn, nor er eyntsiker.

00:09:24.244 --> 00:09:26.347
ven hot ir geheyratet?

00:09:25.662 --> 00:09:29.081
nayn un fertsik, in nayntn khoydesh hob ikh geheyratet.

00:09:28.699 --> 00:09:31.545
un zey hobn nisht gevolt vayter forn fun do?

00:09:31.551 --> 00:09:37.704
mayn man hot gevolt forn keyn s- AUSTRALIA, un ikh hob nisht gevolt forn keyn AUSTRALIA. ikh hob nisht gevolt iberlozn di mame

00:09:38.082 --> 00:09:44.556
gants fun ⟨BEGIN⟩ hob nisht gevolt iberlozn di mame. shpeter hot di mame khasene gehat. ven ikh hob shoyn gehat eyn kind hot di mame khasene gehat.

00:09:44.713 --> 00:09:46.411
oykh in Belgye?

00:09:45.507 --> 00:09:47.948
oykh in Belgye, UNK yo.

00:09:49.388 --> 00:09:51.221
nu, shoyn. dos ze'mir gebli-

00:09:50.046 --> 00:09:53.179
un zey hobn, kinder hobn zey gehat?

00:09:52.830 --> 00:09:55.570
yo, got zay dank. kh'hob bald gehat kinder.

00:09:55.570 --> 00:09:58.440
shpeter bin ikh geganen vegn WIEDERGUTMACHUNG

00:09:58.440 --> 00:10:04.687
hob ikh nisht gevust vos tsu reklamirn, bin ikh dokh gevezn yung, un ikh hob nisht gehat, tsvontsik yor hob ikh shoyn gehat dos kind

00:10:05.402 --> 00:10:07.069
hob ikh f-

00:10:07.069 --> 00:10:08.973
m'hot mir der yeke gefregt

00:10:09.132 --> 00:10:14.242
vu bistu gevezn, SO WEITER, hob ikh ongehoybn aza kleyn bisele tsu fartseyln

00:10:14.242 --> 00:10:16.348
hot er gezogt "vos zol ikh shraybn?

00:10:16.827 --> 00:10:22.238
du host shoyn azoy mitgemakht az dir kumt a groyse rente vos hostu mitgemakht" hot er gezogt.

00:10:23.121 --> 00:10:25.224
vifl kinder hot ir gehat?

00:10:24.673 --> 00:10:28.750
fir kinder hob ikh gehat, tsvey zin mit a, tsvey UNK tekhter.

00:10:27.205 --> 00:10:28.970
vi azoy heysn zey?

00:10:28.943 --> 00:10:35.366
ZIMMER. eyne, di tokhter heyst ⟨STIMMEL⟩ un di eyne hey- tokh- tokhter heyst ⟨ILOWITZ⟩, un di tsvey zin zenen ZIMMER.

00:10:36.182 --> 00:10:38.724
un zey voynen do in Belgye?

00:10:37.363 --> 00:10:42.959
di tsvey ⟨zin⟩ voynen do, un di tokhter voynt, eyne in England un eyne in Amerike.

00:10:43.320 --> 00:10:47.111
un ir hot mit zey geredt iber dem vos ir hot mitgemakht?

00:10:46.830 --> 00:10:49.085
yo. fun anfang nisht.

00:10:49.547 --> 00:10:53.297
di ershte bikhl vos hob ikh gehat iz gevezn HOLOST- -CAU-

00:10:53.297 --> 00:10:55.727
vos i- vos iz gevezn EXODUS

00:10:55.727 --> 00:10:57.568
vos hob ikh ongehoybn tsu lezn

00:10:57.568 --> 00:10:59.779
bin ikh gevezn demolts in KNOKKE

00:10:59.779 --> 00:11:02.420
un ikh hob gelezn. ikh hob dokh dos do mitgemakht

00:11:02.420 --> 00:11:06.340
nisht viln, nisht durkh dem az dos kind iz gezesn, nor ikh bin

00:11:06.340 --> 00:11:09.790
ongehoybn tsu veynen, ongehoybn tsu lezn d- di gantse

00:11:09.790 --> 00:11:11.810
durkhlebn fun di mentshn

00:11:11.890 --> 00:11:14.738
hot er mikh gefregt, demolts hot er gehat akht yor

00:11:14.738 --> 00:11:18.358
UNK dokh mikh gefregt "mame, far vos lezstu a bikhl? du leyenst?"

00:11:18.358 --> 00:11:19.764
zog ikh "yo

00:11:19.990 --> 00:11:27.386
az vest zayn elter, vestu es lezn, vestu es farshteyn. yetst farshteyst. ikh hob gevolt ⟨azolkhn⟩ fartseyln dos do. yetst ken ikh dir nisht fartseyln

00:11:27.386 --> 00:11:29.855
vayl yetst iz gornisht far dir. dos iz a mayse."

00:11:29.997 --> 00:11:33.737
ikh hob zey nisht gelozt lezn keyn bikhl biz zenen zey nisht gevezn

00:11:33.861 --> 00:11:36.740
vi zey hobn aleyn genumen di bikhlekh tsu lezn

00:11:36.898 --> 00:11:42.072
vayl dos hob ikh gezogt, dos iz a zakh vos hot men mitgemakht. dos iz nisht keyn roman.

00:11:42.265 --> 00:11:45.448
dos iz a bitere zakh vos hot men mitgemakht.

00:11:45.167 --> 00:11:48.097
un zey hobn gornisht gefregt, oder

00:11:47.057 --> 00:11:50.645
yo, zey hobn yo gefregt. far vos hobn zey gefregt? vayl ikh hob dem numer.

00:11:50.871 --> 00:11:55.391
az zey zenen gekumen tsu mir in bet arayn, hobn zey eybik gefregt "vos iz der numer? vos iz der numer?"

00:11:55.391 --> 00:11:57.361
hob ikh gezogt "a shlekhter yeke

00:11:57.361 --> 00:12:00.071
hot men dos geshribn," ABER ikh hob zey nisht gevolt fartseyln.

00:12:00.071 --> 00:12:01.563
mir ho'mir nisht gekent redn.

00:12:01.806 --> 00:12:04.916
s'iz gevezn azoy, undz iz bahaltn dos do

00:12:04.916 --> 00:12:08.043
az mir ho'mir nisht gekent dos redn. mir ho'mir dos nisht gekent fartseyln.

00:12:08.472 --> 00:12:11.756
un vos far a ertsiung hot ir gegebn far di kinder?

00:12:10.767 --> 00:12:14.273
ikh hob gegebn a yidishe ertsiung azoy az ikh bin gevezn in di heym.

00:12:14.273 --> 00:12:17.341
fun di ershte minut hot men bay mir geredt yidish in di shtub.

00:12:17.922 --> 00:12:20.835
poylish hob ikh nisht gevolt s- hern mer

00:12:21.938 --> 00:12:24.260
hob ikh bald ongehoybn mit zey yidish.

00:12:25.110 --> 00:12:28.648
zey hobn bakumen a, a religyeze ertsiung?

00:12:27.608 --> 00:12:31.770
ales hobn zey UNK, ale kinder zenen got zay dank frume kinder

00:12:31.894 --> 00:12:34.447
un a sheyne yidishe heym firn zey

00:12:34.447 --> 00:12:38.539
un zey ho- vos hobn zey gezen in di heym, firn zey vayter. iz a ofene shtub

00:12:38.539 --> 00:12:39.988
un ofene hent.

00:12:41.952 --> 00:12:46.131
un zey zenen, zey hobn nakhes. zey hobn eyniklekh?

00:12:43.757 --> 00:12:45.354
yo, got zay dank.

00:12:45.867 --> 00:12:49.911
yo, ikh hob eyniklekh, keyneynehore. zey UNK geyn dem zelbn derekh

00:12:50.136 --> 00:12:52.880
vos, vos hobn zey gezen in shtub.

00:12:53.224 --> 00:12:56.053
bay mir in shtub iz eybik gevezn mentshn.

00:12:56.110 --> 00:13:00.587
eybik geshl- ikh hob nisht gehat keyn groyse WOHNUNG. oyf di ⟨PLANTELE⟩ eyn un tsvontsik hob ikh gevoynt

00:13:00.587 --> 00:13:03.472
hob gehat s- dray shtiblekh, nor kleyne shtiblekh

00:13:03.472 --> 00:13:06.482
iz gekumen, nisht haynt gedakht, iz gevezn a

00:13:06.538 --> 00:13:07.860
POLIO

00:13:07.860 --> 00:13:13.519
a krankeyt. iz gekumen fun Yisroel a yid vos er darf heyln a yid, ⟨darft⟩ er tsuzamennemen gelt.

00:13:13.677 --> 00:13:19.394
hot mayn man hot dos gebrengt in mir in shtub arayn mit fir kinder, a mentsh mit k- a kind mit POLIO krankeyt

00:13:19.394 --> 00:13:21.703
un ikh hob es genumen bay mir in shtub arayn

00:13:21.895 --> 00:13:24.774
un ikh hob es opgehit, un der yid iz ganen nokh gelt.

00:13:25.405 --> 00:13:27.829
iz er geforn keyn Daytshland heyln dos kind

00:13:28.341 --> 00:13:30.219
un stabil gevezn

00:13:30.219 --> 00:13:33.481
di mentshn. ikh hob gevoynt tsveyte tir fun UNK

00:13:34.399 --> 00:13:41.126
un, hot er gezogt azoy, "vi azoy makhstu, mit dayne fir kinder, vi azoy makhstu dos do, az kenst

00:13:41.385 --> 00:13:44.900
kumt, az der mentsh brengt a oyrekh in shtub arayn, hostu eybik"

00:13:44.900 --> 00:13:47.940
zog ikh "vel ikh nisht fray- zuntik nisht esn

00:13:47.940 --> 00:13:50.230
fun shabes, vet men es unterkokhn frish."

00:13:50.230 --> 00:13:52.510
un eybik gevezn far mentshn esn.

00:13:52.520 --> 00:13:53.329
eybik.

00:13:53.329 --> 00:13:55.683
nisht UNK, vayl haynt az

00:13:55.683 --> 00:13:59.058
az me f- kumt a mash- mashgiekh nokh gelt

00:13:59.058 --> 00:14:01.241
kumt nisht in a shtub arayn esn

00:14:01.517 --> 00:14:11.349
nor geyt tsu a reb Yankele, do, dort. demolts iz nisht gevezn. demolts iz men geganen in shtub arayn, un yeder eyner iz arayngekumen ersht in TERLIST shtibl arayn, TERLIST shul

00:14:11.406 --> 00:14:13.661
un er hot eybik gebrengt UNK mentshn.

00:14:14.308 --> 00:14:16.985
ir zent nokh a mol tsurikgeforn keyn

00:14:17.008 --> 00:14:17.795
neyn.

00:14:17.025 --> 00:14:18.099
KRAKAU?

00:14:17.835 --> 00:14:21.305
neyn. ikh bin shoyn nisht mer tsurikgeforn. dos iz UNK

00:14:21.700 --> 00:14:27.501
di kinder betn mir. "mame, k- for, mame for." d- mayn zun iz gevezn, eyner, der tsveyter iz shoyn gevezn

00:14:27.501 --> 00:14:33.053
nisht gevezn tsulib onkukn Poyln, nor iz gekumen forn oyf di kvorim, oyf di heylesh- heylike pletser

00:14:33.053 --> 00:14:36.847
ABER nisht durkh dem onkukn Poyln, vayl dos interesirt im nisht, der Poyln

00:14:37.090 --> 00:14:39.969
nor iz geforn oyf heylike pletser zenen zey geforn.

00:14:40.043 --> 00:14:44.306
der, mayn eltster zun ⟨iz⟩ gevezn dos ershte mol vu der Bobover rebe

00:14:44.397 --> 00:14:47.558
hot oyfgefrisht zayn zeyde matseyve

00:14:47.558 --> 00:14:49.793
vayl zayn tate hot men gesh- geshosn.

00:14:49.793 --> 00:14:52.573
nor zayn zeyde matseyve iz er geforn oyffrishn.

00:14:52.573 --> 00:14:55.993
i- er iz gevezn eyner fun di ershte vos zey zenen mit im mitgeforn.

00:14:55.993 --> 00:14:58.499
mayn man, er iz nokh gevezn a bokher demolts

00:14:58.499 --> 00:15:00.969
nor mayn man hot gevolt di kinder shtupn

00:15:00.969 --> 00:15:03.367
oyf dem yidishn geg- gang

00:15:03.367 --> 00:15:04.527
zoln zey vi- zen

00:15:04.527 --> 00:15:07.377
vayl do in Antverpn iz nisht gevezn demolts nokh azoy fil

00:15:07.853 --> 00:15:10.879
biz s'iz nisht gekumen reb Itsikl UNK

00:15:10.879 --> 00:15:14.099
iz nisht gevezn keyn, ⟨kaza⟩ yidishkeyt do

00:15:14.099 --> 00:15:18.859
hot er geshtupt nor zol geyn, zol geyn, un geshikt bald in di yeshives di kinder

00:15:19.041 --> 00:15:24.148
eyn- eyner hot gemakht RAV UNK yeshive, un eyner hot gemakht PHILADELPHIA yeshive.

00:15:25.133 --> 00:15:27.000
beyde hot men zey gegebn.

00:15:27.597 --> 00:15:29.222
vos

00:15:29.222 --> 00:15:35.707
SIE klern az, hobn SIE moyre az es vet nokh az- ken nokh a mol tsurikkumen aza zakh?

00:15:35.055 --> 00:15:35.988
yo.

00:15:35.988 --> 00:15:36.731
yo.

00:15:36.731 --> 00:15:37.347
yo.

00:15:37.347 --> 00:15:39.386
di yekes zenen oyf dem alts

00:15:39.882 --> 00:15:41.665
ayngeshtelt nokh ales.

00:15:42.092 --> 00:15:45.810
zey zenen, alts eyns zenen mir biter do oyfn plats. biter.

00:15:45.810 --> 00:15:48.735
nokh di krig hob ikh gehat dos ershte kind.

00:15:48.859 --> 00:15:50.591
un dos tsveyte kind

00:15:50.833 --> 00:15:52.990
hob ikh mir gehat azoy in zin

00:15:52.990 --> 00:15:55.130
vos tu ikh? vos tu ikh?

00:15:55.187 --> 00:15:58.640
greyt oyf, vider oyf a ye- oyf a dos do, oyf a khurbn

00:15:59.203 --> 00:16:05.339
vos tu ikh? s'iz nisht keyn, undz dos do greyt men keyn kinder, ober dos velt geyt vayter. me muz boyen undzer dor.

00:16:06.122 --> 00:16:08.647
⟨un⟩ vos iz ayere shaykhes mit Yisroel?

00:16:09.548 --> 00:16:14.739
mayn shaykhes iz zeyer noent mit Yisroel. mayn man iz gevezn zeyer far Yisroel

00:16:15.336 --> 00:16:19.430
frumerheyt, un hot gezogt az yeder yid muz hobn a WOHNUNG in Yisroel

00:16:21.192 --> 00:16:24.673
vayl dos iz undzer plats, un dos vet zayn eybik undzer plats.

00:16:24.673 --> 00:16:28.121
er hot zikh baym lebn gekoyft a plats in Yisroel tsu lign

00:16:28.431 --> 00:16:30.976
un ikh hob a plats in Yisroel tsu lign

00:16:30.976 --> 00:16:32.671
un ⟨nokh⟩ gekoyft a WOHNUNG

00:16:32.671 --> 00:16:34.567
a mayse fun tsvontsik yor

00:16:34.759 --> 00:16:38.752
un halt UNK di WOHNUNG. farkoyf zi nisht, vayl dos iz undzer plats dort tsu zayn.

00:16:39.889 --> 00:16:44.290
vos vilt ir zogn azoy far ayere kinder un di

00:16:44.290 --> 00:16:46.278
nekste doyres als

00:16:46.639 --> 00:16:50.061
moralishe LEKTION vos ir hot ales mitderlebt

00:16:50.061 --> 00:16:52.607
hot ir epes tsu zogn a

00:16:50.419 --> 00:16:55.239
mh eyne iz dos do, iz got BEHUTTE UNK ⟨epes⟩ antloyfn

00:16:55.515 --> 00:16:56.758
vayl undz ze'mir

00:16:56.815 --> 00:16:58.855
vayl undz ze'mir in

00:16:58.855 --> 00:17:03.445
in, vi me zogt in EUROPA in di grestn goles. zey zenen tsu noent bay undz.

00:17:04.223 --> 00:17:06.748
zenen tsu noent far undz. dos iz dos

00:17:07.345 --> 00:17:09.060
der yeke, di DEUTSCHEN.

00:17:09.723 --> 00:17:11.674
undz ze'mir zeyer noent.

00:17:11.732 --> 00:17:13.669
SIE viln nokh epes zogn?

00:17:11.817 --> 00:17:12.587
d-

00:17:13.669 --> 00:17:14.257
do?

00:17:14.314 --> 00:17:17.508
un hofntlekh veln zey geyn in undzer ⟨gegn⟩, di kinder

00:17:17.508 --> 00:17:20.229
azoy vi undzere tate zeydes geganen

00:17:20.288 --> 00:17:22.170
un ikh hof az s'vet alts

00:17:22.170 --> 00:17:24.444
gut zayn, undz zoln mir kenen oyfshteln

00:17:24.444 --> 00:17:27.624
vayter zey zoln shoyn kenen oyfshteln a sheynem dor

00:17:27.624 --> 00:17:29.184
a yidishn ⟨dor⟩ vos undz

00:17:29.184 --> 00:17:32.754
un zey zoln nisht mitmakhn got ⟨BEHUTTE⟩ vos undz hobn mir mitgemakht.

00:17:34.311 --> 00:17:35.840
dos iz vikhtikste

00:17:36.319 --> 00:17:38.523
un gezunterheyt zoln mir vayter zayn.

00:17:39.272 --> 00:17:43.682
vayl leyder, leyder, far di l- mentshn vos zenen gevezn in lager vos zey hobn mitgemakht dos

00:17:43.682 --> 00:17:46.852
di zakhn, zenen ale kra- krank oyf ALZHEIMER.

00:17:47.288 --> 00:17:50.555
ale zenen zey krank, az dos, dos iz geblibn in dem kop

00:17:51.085 --> 00:17:54.026
zey hobn moyre far dem, un dos ken men nisht trefn keyn

00:17:54.026 --> 00:17:57.187
keyn retung oyf dem. dos iz ergste vi ales.

00:17:58.493 --> 00:18:04.309
zey hobn moyre far dem. mayn ⟨mame⟩ iz oykhet gevorn oyf ALZHEIMER. s'iz takesh avekgeganen in

00:18:04.382 --> 00:18:08.578
in di rikhtike yorn, vi me zogt, dos hot ⟨zi⟩ gehat nayn un akhtsik yor

00:18:09.529 --> 00:18:12.791
ABER yednfal hot zi gekent avekgeyn gezunterheyt

00:18:12.791 --> 00:18:17.555
nisht oyf di ALZHEIMER. iz zi tsen yor gevezn nebekh krank vos zi hot shoyn gornisht ⟨gevust ver undz ze'mir⟩

00:18:18.085 --> 00:18:21.420
iz gevezn a froy vos hot zeyer a sakh getun

00:18:21.696 --> 00:18:27.911
iz gevezn di agude. zi hot oyfgeshtelt di ershte agude, sh- gekoyft dos hoyz, hot men gek- oyf di z-

00:18:27.911 --> 00:18:30.954
VAN LERIUS. zey hobn nokh nisht gehat keyn gelt

00:18:31.078 --> 00:18:33.063
hot zi shoyn gekoyft dos hoyz.

00:18:33.154 --> 00:18:35.679
shpeter hot zi oykh geshtelt di tsveyte agude

00:18:36.428 --> 00:18:39.392
gekoyft dos hoyz, iz zi hot zeyer a sakh ge-

00:18:39.398 --> 00:18:40.354
⟨gevet⟩

00:18:40.495 --> 00:18:45.231
iz zi hot gevezn eybik tikhtik, biz, di gantse yorn gevezn tikhtik in di agude

00:18:45.355 --> 00:18:50.878
mit di MADAME UNK, mit MADAME, farshidene froyen fun di AGUDE, iz zi gevezn eyn eyntsike nokh.

00:18:50.878 --> 00:18:53.296
demolts hot nokh keyner nisht getrogn keyn sheytl

00:18:54.012 --> 00:18:56.149
un m'iz gevezn oykhet in di agude.

00:18:59.108 --> 00:18:59.945
CA VA.

00:18:59.732 --> 00:19:01.295
MERCI, ⟨MAMAN⟩.

00:19:00.542 --> 00:19:01.380
⟨VA⟩

00:19:04.677 --> 00:19:07.759
vem zet men do oyf dem bild?

00:19:06.533 --> 00:19:11.862
dos iz dem, di bild vos ikh bin gevezn in di klas mit mayn shvester tsuzamen.

00:19:11.862 --> 00:19:15.034
ikh bin oyf di tsveyte reye. zi iz oyf di ershte reye

00:19:15.034 --> 00:19:19.267
vayl ikh bin gevezn a sakh greser fun ir. zi iz gevezn oyf di ershte reye. zi iz

00:19:19.290 --> 00:19:22.169
iz di tsveyte VON, fun di links.

00:19:24.387 --> 00:19:27.722
dos iz gevezn in di tsveyte klas in di shule.

00:19:28.116 --> 00:19:30.050
dos iz gevezn

00:19:31.862 --> 00:19:35.113
iz akht un, zibn un draysik.

00:19:35.406 --> 00:19:36.918
tsveyte klas.

00:19:38.140 --> 00:19:39.163
zeks un

00:19:41.515 --> 00:19:45.609
dos iz mayn tate. ne- er iz nebekh nifter gevorn in MAUTHAUSEN.

00:19:46.105 --> 00:19:48.377
fun ven iz dos bild? veyst ir?

00:19:48.062 --> 00:19:52.353
dos iz, undz ho'mir gemakht dos fun a kleyn bite- bild fun a

00:19:52.353 --> 00:19:58.924
vos iz gevezn in STADT hoyz, hobn mir aroysgekrign UNK bild, un dos hot men gemakht a groys. velkhes yor veys ikh nisht.

00:19:59.402 --> 00:20:01.724
vem zet men do oyf dem bild?

00:20:00.702 --> 00:20:04.689
do oyf dem foto iz mayn mame vos zitst oyfn benkl

00:20:04.689 --> 00:20:09.504
un di dray meydlekh zenen mir geganen tsuzamen in di reye oyfn toyter marsh.

00:20:10.000 --> 00:20:15.782
un di mame iz, mikh hot zi nisht gelozt geyn, vayl ikh bin gevezn imer di kind vos hot gemuzt blaybn in di shtub.

00:20:15.900 --> 00:20:17.670
vi heysn di meydlekh?

00:20:17.442 --> 00:20:20.811
dos gedenk ikh nisht. dos veys ikh nisht dem nomen oykhet.

00:20:20.226 --> 00:20:22.760
un hobn zey iberlebt UNK?

00:20:21.643 --> 00:20:26.800
zey hobn iberlebt, un zey zenen geforn in lager arayn tsu mayn shvester dort keyn

00:20:26.925 --> 00:20:29.521
un dort zey hobn getrofn mayn shvester tsu zogn

00:20:29.521 --> 00:20:31.914
UNK

00:20:33.321 --> 00:20:37.196
MADAME ZIMMER, vem zet men do oyf dem bild?

00:20:35.802 --> 00:20:40.675
dos iz bald nokh di krig, dos iz mayn onkl, UNK heyst er

00:20:40.675 --> 00:20:46.624
nokh di krig ven iz er gevezn nokh in MAUTHAUSEN, un, un er leyder hot gebrengt mayn, undz di nayes

00:20:46.624 --> 00:20:49.936
az me ta- mayn tate iz dort gevezn, iz dort geshtorbn.

00:20:49.960 --> 00:20:51.760
un vu shteyt er do?

00:20:51.968 --> 00:20:56.501
do shteyt er farn, farn UNK hot men gefirt in krematoryum di mentshn.

00:20:58.768 --> 00:21:01.749
ven hot men dos oyfgenumen, un vem zet men UNK?

00:21:01.333 --> 00:21:04.955
do zet men mayn man un mir, UNK bay di khasene

00:21:05.063 --> 00:21:07.014
in nayn un fertsik.

00:21:07.773 --> 00:21:09.853
vu iz dos geven?

00:21:08.539 --> 00:21:11.182
dos iz in Antverpn gevezn di khasene.

00:21:11.239 --> 00:21:13.157
nayn un fertsik september.

00:21:15.137 --> 00:21:18.253
ven iz dos gevezn, un ver zenen di damen?

00:21:16.605 --> 00:21:20.154
dos iz, dos iz in tsvey un zibetsik

00:21:20.154 --> 00:21:24.192
ven hob ikh khasene gehat, gemakht mayn sh- tokhter khasene

00:21:24.418 --> 00:21:30.254
di ILOWITZ fun Amerike, oyf di, un do in di mit shteyt mayn mame, un fun eyn zayt shteyt mayn shvester

00:21:30.254 --> 00:21:33.440
in geln kleyd, un ikh bin in dem ⟨gemostn⟩ kleyd.

00:21:35.620 --> 00:21:37.619
ver iz di dame do?

00:21:35.809 --> 00:21:44.032
dos di, dos iz, eyn foto iz di muter, un di tsveyte foto iz di tsvey shvestern, dos iz fun mayn man zayn muter

00:21:44.032 --> 00:21:46.333
leyder keyner nisht mer nisht geblibn.

00:21:46.558 --> 00:21:51.699
dos iz nokh, di foto fun far di krig vos hobn mir gehat gekrign fun Yisroel fun UNK mentshn.

00:21:54.338 --> 00:21:57.639
do zet men a bild., vos iz dos?

00:21:57.763 --> 00:22:00.406
do zet men a bild vos ma- mayn man

00:22:00.447 --> 00:22:05.455
hot geganen mit dem shvung z- nor tsu gebn gute zakhn makhn

00:22:05.455 --> 00:22:07.511
hot khasene gemakht di kinder

00:22:07.602 --> 00:22:12.020
got zay dank mit mazl, mit gezunt. zenen ale got zay dank gliklekh

00:22:12.020 --> 00:22:14.914
hot er gezogt yetst muz er shraybn a seyfer toyre.

00:22:14.914 --> 00:22:19.391
dos iz far zayne eltern un far mayn tatn, UNK vos iz nebekh avek

00:22:19.583 --> 00:22:20.825
in di krig.

00:22:20.983 --> 00:22:26.225
ale zenen zey avek, un dos iz ge- seyfer toyre iz gevorn gegebn in TERLIST besmedresh

00:22:26.282 --> 00:22:29.130
oyfn nomen fun di eltern

00:22:29.130 --> 00:22:31.915
ABER dos kind- gehert tsu di kinder.

00:22:31.915 --> 00:22:35.965
yetst az s'iz, biz yetst iz gevezn TERLIST besmedresh.

00:22:35.965 --> 00:22:39.465
yetst hot men aroysgenumen di seyfer toyre fun TERLIST besmedresh

00:22:39.465 --> 00:22:40.785
hot men gegebn

00:22:40.785 --> 00:22:42.535
in Bobover shule

00:22:42.535 --> 00:22:49.024
vayl di kinder y- zenen shoyn dort fun draytsn yor, vos zey hobn yetst ⟨baginen⟩ tsu leyenen, un dos blaybt yetst far zey tsu z- leyenen

00:22:49.024 --> 00:22:50.954
un dort zenen mayne eyniklekh.

00:22:52.506 --> 00:22:53.259
UNK

00:22:54.919 --> 00:22:57.370
vem zet men do oyf dem bild?

00:22:56.353 --> 00:23:02.577
do zet men reb Yankele n- reb Yankele vos er trogt di seyfer toyre

00:23:02.577 --> 00:23:05.156
un mayn man t- tantst akegn

00:23:05.314 --> 00:23:06.956
bay di seyfer toyre.

00:23:06.956 --> 00:23:12.446
dos iz oyf di gas, oyf di TERLIST STRASSE. m'hot aroysgenumen ale seyfer toyres fun besmedresh

00:23:12.807 --> 00:23:14.997
un dos iz a zeyer groyser koved

00:23:14.997 --> 00:23:16.667
tsu gebn a seyfer toyre

00:23:16.667 --> 00:23:18.837
far undz, far yidn, UNK dos vet blaybn

00:23:18.853 --> 00:23:21.001
oyf ⟨doyrn, doyrn⟩ vayter

00:23:21.126 --> 00:23:22.723
lesholem UNK

00:23:26.205 --> 00:23:29.608
tsu velkhe gelegnheyt iz gemakht gevorn di

00:23:28.585 --> 00:23:33.838
dos foto iz gemakht far tsvey yor. mayn eynikl hot shoyn khasene gemakht. dos heyst shoyn

00:23:33.838 --> 00:23:37.236
az s'iz shoyn, mayn mame hot shoyn nisht gelebt

00:23:37.410 --> 00:23:40.475
ABER s'iz shoyn der fifter dor nokh di krig.

00:23:41.038 --> 00:23:43.296
un ver zenen di ⟨andere mentshn⟩?

00:23:42.253 --> 00:23:44.997
di ale arum un arum zenen mayne kinder.

00:23:45.223 --> 00:23:50.920
mayne kinder un mayne eyniklekh. fun VORNE shteyen mayne kinder, un do arum un arum shteyen shoyn di eyniklekh

00:23:50.995 --> 00:23:53.621
mit di shnurs mit di eydems.

00:23:55.028 --> 00:24:00.239
dos iz, dos iz shoyn a, a ⟨doyre⟩ vos vet blay- zol vayter blaybn oyf ale lebn.
